  <item>
   <title>Version 1.5.3+1</title>
   <pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 18:03:27 +0000</pubDate>
   <description>Version 1.5.3

- Harden the Windows auto-update flow by keeping the updater feed fixed per session and adding explicit trigger/completion timeout handling.
- Persist manual update diagnostics, add dedicated auto-update metrics, and improve the Settings UI technical details for support scenarios.
- Add DSA-signing support to the installer/release pipeline and embed the WinSparkle public key resource for future signed appcast publishing.
- Release includes the Windows installer asset PlugAgente-Setup-1.5.3.exe.</description>
